{"tid":215874,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"漫畫技法","createTime":"2017-04-24T16:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T05:04:39.000Z","uid":42119,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de50339b9004941998cb396dac9e95647290e7e7","tid":215874,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"連登有冇漫畫家? 想了解更多畫漫畫既技巧<br />\n<br />\n大家初初係點學呢D技巧? 無師自通?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係有參考書<br />\n<br />\n最近開始認真去諗點解作者會咁畫，線條有咩效果，格同格之間既關係，越睇就越覺得漫畫技法好深奧，好多要素不知不覺隱藏左<br />\n漫畫家真係千錘百鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我求其CAP一幅舉例<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b11Fi4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb11Fi4g.jpg&h=d79275f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣已經包含左好多技巧係入面<br />\n大家都知日本漫畫係右至左，上至下睇<br />\n1)第2格一下講晒&quot;起因&quot;<br />\n2)1，3，5格就係男主角踩單車，用線條表達速度感，格越黎越大表示進展，第3)3格用細長格再加強速度（由右至左，符合讀者習慣）<br />\n4)用集中線同對話框營造緊張感<br />\n5)擬聲詞<br />\n6)用緊張感襯托男主踩單車好快<br />\n真係越睇越有味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漫畫家係咪都係怪物<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識畫漫畫，但算係睇得多"},{"pid":"31114a484b264e5d970679603a8c3b61a9c381b7","tid":215874,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:57:57.000Z","msg":"畫功 分鏡 劇情 對白 刻畫人物性格 線條 <br />\n<br />\n漫畫係好高深  淨係畫已經好難"},{"pid":"51c6e9045e3904bf57ae4b42cdf2b03775fa21dd","tid":215874,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"咁你睇下烙印戰士既漫畫<br />\n我覺得係神級作畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b802b86f940672ebab160f4fed899d20a542171b","tid":215874,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:07:49.000Z","msg":"可以學下袁生"},{"pid":"c7187b5a68051b1e7565c240bd30c032f4199fb9","tid":215874,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"香港得猿生配叫做漫畫家<br />\n其他都係垃圾"},{"pid":"e24a819c8db4a6705930f825c78502473b5117d3","tid":215874,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"格同格之間既關係,其實動畫電影都有,即係唔同分鏡,只係漫畫每格唔識活動,可以用線條去同擬聲詞去表達個動作"},{"pid":"4c91cf803d7a7544be34161acc74c71706500363","tid":215874,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你睇下烙印戰士既漫畫<br />\n我覺得係神級作畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無例圖分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268bdded9907fd58d91cc2768c255ae34167a4c9","tid":215874,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁你睇下烙印戰士既漫畫<br />\n我覺得係神級作畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無例圖分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/fdpCpVzYGmY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FfdpCpVzYGmY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=5061e986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e356a7083b493260d967e6e614111d9c9c0f2a2f","tid":215874,"uid":40425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:30:32.000Z","msg":"香港著名漫畫家袁生都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好打極好限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e9f0b20779a1ce63ad6d80e0264eabf2325c3e","tid":215874,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港著名漫畫家袁生都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好打極好限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點啊 你係咪佢三個acc其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dfc4b6a4b408c3772998789628edf2f81147f1","tid":215874,"uid":107623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"烙印戰士，孤高之人，純真之人。毋庸置疑嘅好畫工。<br />\n<br />\n海賊王其實啲畫都好用心同好多考慮。當然意見好兩極。有啲人會覺得鳩塞同埋亂七八糟。但平時畫畫多嘅人會知道佢嘅畫作難係邊啲位。"},{"pid":"6022fc21fec6e65b163b28d8eb53fadf5704d60d","tid":215874,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:22:30.000Z","msg":"岸本d技巧係咪算好top"},{"pid":"691564c4bdc4e269b52b66c2af426e6dca83bb91","tid":215874,"uid":7752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T20:19:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岸本d技巧係咪算好top</blockquote><br />\n分鏡一流"},{"pid":"ec1c5c38a5ee5cd73bb4112fc8bdb05906829f40","tid":215874,"uid":34293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T00:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1z8w97gp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1z8w97gp&h=abbca56d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fdc6d70b81aaf28614dfb7d05ded4e6a6bec354","tid":215874,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岸本d技巧係咪算好top</blockquote><br />\n分鏡一流</blockquote><br />\n岸本分鏡係冇得輸"},{"pid":"09ed893e26b568bd3b0947417f5f2282a17e7193","tid":2