5910932.jpg&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9cebd339\" target=\"_blank\">http://upload.shunwang.com/2013/0702/1372735910932.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n岸本畫呢啲應該會再好啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實呢幅其實唔算好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依幅只可以話構圖ok，但分鏡嚟講冇上面幾張冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果d神枱級梗係無得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過近幾年黎講排球d分鏡算幾有氣勢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只計呢張，我只會認為佢係跟左幅真人低炒打波相黎畫</blockquote><br />\n亞人分鏡都好撚勁"},{"pid":"a2afa6146943dc32e20d5add22c875bb94bdfeb8","tid":215874,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烙印戰士，孤高之人，純真之人。毋庸置疑嘅好畫工。<br />\n<br />\n海賊王其實啲畫都好用心同好多考慮。當然意見好兩極。有啲人會覺得鳩塞同埋亂七八糟。但平時畫畫多嘅人會知道佢嘅畫作難係邊啲位。</blockquote><br />\n海賊王難唔難畫係一回事，但塞爆晒真係好影響閱讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得就算畫工再好，分鏡差都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但偏偏而家既OP塞爆就造成左問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞爆字造成讀者無法掌握節奏，塞爆圖令立體感無左之餘又突出唔到每格重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YVrT9j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YVrT9j.jpg&h=45602bd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c86dfad9890fa0f6f9e4fd5ff74aeba7c8492b0","tid":215874,"uid":34058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得分鏡好嘅仲有 亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c016702116a53eaf3e6cc3cbe25c167d719abb3","tid":215874,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得分鏡好嘅仲有 亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger 近年最好"},{"pid":"bdef2e1a8efdfb04f89c42b4325a4247a8d91a7e","tid":215874,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>烙印戰士，孤高之人，純真之人。毋庸置疑嘅好畫工。<br />\n<br />\n海賊王其實啲畫都好用心同好多考慮。當然意見好兩極。有啲人會覺得鳩塞同埋亂七八糟。但平時畫畫多嘅人會知道佢嘅畫作難係邊啲位。</blockquote><br />\n海賊王難唔難畫係一回事，但塞爆晒真係好影響閱讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得就算畫工再好，分鏡差都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但偏偏而家既OP塞爆就造成左問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞爆字造成讀者無法掌握節奏，塞爆圖令立體感無左之餘又突出唔到每格重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YVrT9j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YVrT9j.jpg&h=45602bd5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢已經走火入魔啦，套野岩岩出個陣佢用返龍珠既風格令人睇落好簡潔舒服，但佢個世界觀發展到呢部要整到好華麗加夢幻，所以所有野都要愈來愈精細，搞到而家突出唔到個重點，但未來故事發展都一定會走向黑暗化，唔知會唔會更加令到畫面雜亂呢"},{"pid":"3a6c63d6ec630cd1b9f7f9d43c85d38d7cd63d9d","tid":215874,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n海賊王難唔難畫係一回事，但塞爆晒真係好影響閱讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得就算畫工再好，分鏡差都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但偏偏而家既OP塞爆就造成左問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞爆字造成讀者無法掌握節奏，塞爆圖令立體感無左之餘又突出唔到每格重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/8YVrT9j.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YVrT9j.jpg&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=49837ab6\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/8YVrT9j.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢已經走火入魔啦，套野岩岩出個陣佢用返龍珠既風格令人睇落好簡潔舒服，但佢個世界觀發展到呢部要整到好華麗加夢幻，所以所有野都要愈來愈精細，搞到而家突出唔到個重點，但未來故事發展都一定會走向黑暗化，唔知會唔會更加令到畫面雜亂呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海賊王構圖真係鍾意一格格都塞到滿晒，好似依張圖左下角嗰格，一眼望埋去已經唔想仔細睇。<br />\n明明唔係故事重點，你畫咁多兵仔塞滿一格做乜，玩緊威利在哪裡？"},{"pid":"32046f5161316e714e2dad645701567ff6f8145c","tid":215874,"uid":49398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n海賊王難唔難畫係一回事，但塞爆晒真係好影響閱讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得就算畫工再好，分鏡差都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但偏偏而家既OP塞爆就造成左問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞爆字造成讀者無法掌握節奏，塞爆圖令立體感無左之餘又突出唔到每格重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/8YVrT9j.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YVrT9j.jpg&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9ELwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=49837ab6\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/8YVrT9j.jpg</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢已經走火入魔啦，套野岩岩出個陣佢用返龍珠既風格令人睇落好簡潔舒服，但佢個世界觀發展到呢部要整到好華麗加夢幻，所以所有野都要愈來愈精細，搞到而家突出唔到個重點，但未來故事發展都一定會走向黑暗化，唔知會唔會更加令到畫面雜亂呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海賊王構圖真係鍾意一格格都塞到滿晒，好似依張圖左下角嗰格，一眼望埋去已經唔想仔細睇。<br />\n明明唔係故事重點，你畫咁多兵仔塞滿一格做乜，玩緊威利在哪裡？</blockquote><br />\n我都覺對白同畫面失晒平衡, <br />\n宜家睇已經要掛住睇字而唔理畫緊乜, 甚至唔知佢畫緊乜"},{"pid":"37a322f077f5c9860d1849430f98f8e1cff57a2a","tid":215874,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>排球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://upload.shunwang.com/2013/0702/1372735910932.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?